10 An Act relating to sunsets; amending 59 O.S. 2021,
Section 1354, as last amended by Section 1, Chapter
11 265, O.S.L. 2025 (59 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 1354),
which relates to the State Board of Examiners of
12 Psychologists; modifying sunset date; repealing 63
O.S. 2021, Section 1-1923, as amended by Section 1,
13 Chapter 197, O.S.L. 2023 (63 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section
1-1923), which relates to the Long-Term Care Facility
14 Advisory Council; providing an effective date; and
